Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙呢 遙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你丟下了遙是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}\N  \N重 \N \N  \N演 \N \N \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉的侵蝕變的嚴重起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空可能也會發生因果定律的審判
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 或許已經發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果定律的審判...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 究竟在說什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解釋的讓我能明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指原因和結果逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因和結果逆轉?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說過去要受到未來的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去要受到未來的影響?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的事情忘記了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說只是幻影而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉才不是什麼幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來試一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉一直在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備把龍之轉矩怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是會死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年後的佑就是鴉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎~已經七點半啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個我?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 早飯已經做好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 幾點了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經8點多了哦 我要去上學了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再睡一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是第一學期最後的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是浮游靈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和它說話了 就會被它拖進靈界去了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像討論的很熱烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保的超常現象解說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴聲已經響了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回座位 回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假活動在班會結束以後再討論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪惠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 藤原君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假和我約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾 約會的日程都已經排滿到三年後了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得稍微...有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（下課時間 回家路上請小心）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這樣就決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原也要一起去哦 試膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為..為什麼啊 試膽量什麼的我才不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我還有私塾 所以不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原 你可一定要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說藤原君是膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕的尿出來很丟人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你說什麼 向井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說中了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做感覺很不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 佑那傢伙 最近都不怎麼合群了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤要參加中學考試的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雖然是那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總覺得稍微...有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艘好船吧 一艘就要兩千五百億日元呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不是客船 所以乘坐的感覺要差上那麼一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篠原君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你不也很想看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是約好了終止這項實驗的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀~是這麼回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概我沒有說過要停止這回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你不也接受了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是應該是正式的報酬...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 我這邊也付了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望至少要賺回我應得的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡都是些光說不幹的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在築波的現場失敗了三回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說5人都被開除了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我已經沒有關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是要做的 就這樣一直做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣再做下去只會讓θ粒子分散掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在東京看實驗的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓這個地域整個崩潰掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 黛博士的女兒好像是住在這附近的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 我們一起來看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越時間和空間的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 去了佑的私塾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在私塾前面等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚還出來 會被綁架的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那麼擔心我 就不要離家出走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你說要離家出走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你說想去東京的父親那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候是和媽媽吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家父母又離婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況很複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信以為真的我才是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佑 不要生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算離家出走了 也只不過是很快就被找到帶回家罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等成為大人了 什麼地方都可以去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我不是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭當小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 想快點變成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我變的不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 也不用推我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 明天一起離家出走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是約好了的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要一起離家出走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去爸爸那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像...忘記了什麼重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你爸爸聯繫上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是被說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為離家出走的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離家出走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個時空就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空是你所選擇的時空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所選擇的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然鴉是來自未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他一定是另一個佑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直保護著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知什麼時候鴉從我面前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為佑應該只有一個才對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再一次..被遙救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那場戰鬥裡 我應該死了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉到地面上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉到左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行 前進的道路被妨礙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉飛進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 要崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過時空的狹縫所來到的就是這個時空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我沒有察覺到那個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我轉移到了一個近似的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為被吸到了這個時空才得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為我轉移到了這個時空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉庫裡瑪才知道了這個時空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才知道了遙的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 還可能喚醒另一個時空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以遙為目標...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了 要出來了 我感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了 向井 感覺很不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 要與幽靈大人見面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加認真一些 藤原君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真要怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從心底祈禱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈大人 幽靈大人 請快快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒搞錯吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在擔心後藤嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊 他們家又不會允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來喲 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 要跟不上美保他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我似乎忘記了一件非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 在見到幽靈之前決不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛 有什麼不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 墓地裡不應該沒有幽靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 大家快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼飛過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃 快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是靈 是地縛靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 是沖著我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和這個時空的自己同化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 和我一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了我的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 去了香格里拉你就會想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 就是...你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是我該待的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我忘記了重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在這裡和鴉相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那之前見過鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春天即將來臨的那個下雪天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空歪曲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你又來救我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒...沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.90,0:24:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.87,0:24:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏日的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.29,0:24:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我消失也沒有關係
